(4, 'When are ‘Returns’ not possible?', 'Whenever your products have been used for more than 15 days.'),
(5, 'What are the items that cannot be returned?', '<p>The items that can not be returned are:</p><p>Clearance items clearly marked as such and displaying a No-Return Policy<br></p><p>When the offer notes states so specifically are items that cannot be returned.</p><p><br></p>');

